OL,6,FOne person died and seven people were
OL,7,Fcritically injured as severe
OL,8,Fturbulence struck a Singapore Airlines
OL,9,Fflight from Heathrow Airport, ITV
OL,10,FNews' Martha Fairlie reports
OL,12,FA British man has died and seven
OL,13,Fothers left critically injured after a
OL,14,FLondon to Singapore flight was hit by
OL,15,Fsevere turbulence on Tuesday.
OL,17,FThe man has been identified as 73-year-
OL,18,Fold Geoffrey Ralph Kitchen, a .
