OL,6,FSingapore Airlines, the airline that
OL,7,Foperated the flight, confirmed that 18
OL,8,Fpeople in total had been hospitalised.
OL,9,FOther passengers and crew members are
OL,10,Fbeing examined and receiving treatment
OL,11,Fwhere needed.
OL,13,FThe plane had to be diverted to
OL,14,FBangkok, Thailand, at 3.45pm local
OL,15,Ftime (9.45am UK time) on Tuesday.
OL,17,FAndrew Davies was among the 47 British
OL,18,Fpassengers on board the flight.
