OL,6,FBusinessman Andrew Davies, who was on
OL,7,Fboard the Singapore Airlines flight,
OL,8,Ftold ITV News about the on board
OL,9,Fexperience
OL,11,FHe left London Heathrow at 10pm on
OL,12,FMonday to take his regular flight to
OL,13,FNew Zealand, via Singapore, and
OL,14,Fdescribed the flight as 'normal'
OL,15,Fbefore the turbulence hit.
