OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Mr Davies said:
OL,7,F"About six or seven hours into the
OL,8,Fflight I was watching a film and the
OL,9,Fseatbelt sign came on so I put my
OL,10,Fseatbelt on and literally in seconds,
OL,11,Fof putting it on there was a sudden
OL,12,Fthud."
OL,14,FHe described how passenger belongings,
OL,15,Fincluding "cushions, pillows, blankets
OL,16,Fand laptops", were flying around the
OL,17,Faircraft.
