OL,6,FWhilst a lot of people on board were
OL,7,Fin distress, Mr Davies felt the cabin
OL,8,Fcrew were "incredible" throughout the
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,F"Out of all the cabin crew, even those
OL,12,Fwho were injured they were all helping
OL,13,Fpeople. Even if they had (facial)
OL,14,Flacerations, they carried on doing
OL,15,Ftheir work to the best of their
OL,16,Fability.
OL,18,F"I was very impressed about how hard
OL,19,Fthey worked."
