OL,6,FThe statement said: "We can confirm
OL,7,Fthat there are injuries and one
OL,8,Ffatality on board the Boeing 777-
OL,9,F300ER. There were a total of 211
OL,10,Fpassengers and 18 crew on board.
OL,12,F"Singapore Airlines offers its deepest
OL,13,Fcondolences to the family of the
OL,14,Fdeceased."
