OL,6,FFlightradar24 said its tracking data
OL,7,Fshowed the plane encountering
OL,8,Fturbulence at approximately 8.49am BST
OL,9,Fwhile flying over Myanmar.
OL,11,FThe flight tracking service said data
OL,12,Fsent from the aircraft showed a "rapid
OL,13,Fchange in vertical rate, consistent
OL,14,Fwith a sudden turbulence event",
OL,15,Fadding that there were "some severe"
OL,16,Fthunderstorms in the area at the time.
OL,18,FFootage shows a number of ambulances
OL,19,Fleaving Suvarnabhumi airport in
OL,20,FBangkok where the flight was diverted
OL,21,Fand passengers placed on stretchers
