OL,6,F"There are discussions about whether
OL,7,Fclimate change is influencing an
OL,8,Fincrease in occurrences."
OL,10,FMr Strickland said airlines use a
OL,11,Fvariety of methods to minimise the
OL,12,Fchances of a flight being affected by
OL,13,Fturbulence, such as weather forecasts,
OL,14,Fradar and reports from aircraft ahead.
OL,16,FHe added: "It can never be taken
OL,17,Flightly when airlines recommended you
OL,18,Fkeep the seatbelt loosely fastened
OL,19,Fthroughout the flight."
